                                "answer": "All our products are delivered instantly. After payment validation, you will receive your access or boosts directly on the site, via Discord, or by email. If you need help, join our __DISCORD__."
                            },
                            {
                                "question": "What are the official contact methods?",
                                "answer": "We are mainly available on __DISCORD__ and __TELEGRAM__. Beware of imposters — only use the official links shown here and in our site footer."
                            },
                            {
                                "question": "Are the services guaranteed?",
                                "answer": "Yes, we offer warranties on our products. Specific warranty details and durations are mentioned in the description of each product. Our 24\/7 support is also available for any assistance."
                            },
                            {
                                "question": "Do you offer discounts for bulk orders?",
                                "answer": "Absolutely! Contact us on __TELEGRAM__ or open a ticket on __DISCORD__ to discuss bulk pricing for your large orders."
                            },
                            {
                                "question": "How can I contact support if I have a problem?",
                                "answer": "Our dedicated support team is available 24\/7. You can reach us by opening a ticket on our __DISCORD__ server or messaging us on __TELEGRAM__. We guarantee a response to all inquiries."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
